<li>Sending you strength and love as you navigate this profound loss.</li>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss. Your mother was a wonderful person.</li>
<li>May the love and memories you shared bring you comfort during this painful time.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, I offer my deepest condolences.</li>
<li>She will always be remembered for her (mention a positive trait, like her generosity or humor).</li>
<li>Your mother's legacy will live on through your love and memories.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincere condolences.  May her soul rest in peace.</li>
<li>Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers during this sad time.</li>
<li>May the happy memories you shared bring solace in the coming days.</li>
